{
  "stem": "12564.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I'm looking outside to see a duck is holding the bag, the sack.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he's still eating.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So I jumped on him.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And it's left over, one piece.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So the duck walked away.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "He wasn't hungry.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So he didn't bite me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I came back with one piece of bread.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Until late in the night.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Then I returned to the place.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "By the end of 1943, these people didn't want to hold us any longer.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were afraid.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we went to another Polish family, but they did not have any food to give us.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So the only food what we can organize is to go around like I did.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "One day, me and my brother went.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we figured, we'll bring food, whatever we can.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we took ourselves green peas, what they were keeping under a house, to dry.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So we took sheets.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We put the green peas inside.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Yeah, green peas it was.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we carried on the shoulder like inexperienced thieves.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And probably we were leaving signs.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Until the next day in the morning, we hear something, a noise outside.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We were in the attic.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "We're looking down.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Guys with such a long sticks, and said, we'll have to kill these thieves.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "They didn't know who did it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And they came actually into the barn.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And I was that time, me, my brother-- we both brought the green peas-- and mother.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "The split decision was to rip off the roof.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "It was a straw roof.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Me and my brother jumped down.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And we run away.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "The caught my mother.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "They didn't do nothing to mother, but they knew that we escaped.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
